    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="next">&rsaquo;</a>
-->
</div><!-- /.carousel -->

<div class="content-wrapper" id="body">

    <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
    <div class="row">
      <div class="container marketing">
        <div class="span4">
            <h2>Sharing</h2>
            <p>Sharing should be rewarding. Your grandmother wants to see her grandchild's precious moments and not social network security policy.</p>

        </div><!-- /.span4 -->
        <div class="span4">
            <h2>Simple</h2>
            <p>Upload your family moments now. The simple interface lets you add pictures directly from you smartphone, tablet, or computer. There is no waiting to update client software just to get to your pictures.</p>

        </div><!-- /.span4 -->
        <div class="span4">
            <h2>Security</h2>
            <p>You can't replace lost pictures. Back them up now. Take control of your images. You are not the product. You are the customer.</p>

        </div><!-- /.span4 -->
    </div>
 </div><!-- /.row -->
</div>
</div> <!==! end of .content-wrapper" id="body">
